this is my first prefab it is for anyone that is making a greek map and wants to spice it up a bit this is just a small section of the aquaduct so copy paste it as much as you need. i also added in a old ladder you don't need to use it but if you want to get on top for good sniping i would use that. it can be used for a virety of things so be created if you are smart you can also use the columns for pillars :)

happy mapping :)
